1. *Centi* su najmanja novčana jedinica u Srbiji. ( *Centi* are the smallest monetary unit in Serbia.)
2. Danas sam pronašao *centi* na ulici. (Today I found some *cents* on the street.)
3. Cena ovog proizvoda iznosi 299 *centi*. (The price of this product is 299 *cents*.)
4. Ovo voće košta 50 *centi* po komadu. (This fruit costs 50 *cents* per piece.)
5. Kupio sam dve kugle sladoleda za 120 *centi*. (I bought two scoops of ice cream for 120 *cents*.)
6. Nisam imao dovoljno *centi* da platim parkiranje. (I didn't have enough *cents* to pay for parking.)
7. *Centi* su deo metričkog sistema za merenje dužine. (*Centi* are part of the metric system for measuring length.)
8. Ova kabanica je vodootporna do 1000 *centi*metara. (This raincoat is waterproof up to 1000 *centi*meters.)
9. Deca su pokušala da naprave kulu od *centi*ma. (The kids tried to build a tower out of *cents*.)
10. Stavio sam novčić od 50 *centi* u aparat za sok. (I put a 50 *cent* coin in the vending machine for a soda.)